title: NFT MARKET LISITING SUGGESTION “bunks” (a full 1:1 fork of crypto punks)
body:
Bunks is community-driven project on bsc that promotes nfts to all of those who missed the opportunity of the original collection. They are one of the inspirations for many other bsc nft forks.


Official telegram: (https://t.me/binancepunkscommunity)

Marketplace: https://nftkey.app/collections/bunks/

Official website: https://bscbunks.com/

Meme twitter: https://twitter.com/bscbunks

Contract: 0x5ea899dbc8d3cde806142a955806e06759b05fb8

Coin type: bep20



Why binance punks exist: the initial crypto punks distribution was free to claim punks. 
This made it so that a few early nft fans had all the fun and have made millions. Now many more people are aware of nfts. We want to give everyone on bsc a chance to be a part of history!

Crypto punks are unaffordable, but bunks are for everyone.



Binance bunks are the first full nft fork ever created on the bsc, and are a full 1:1 fork of crypto punks. 

Crypto punks were initially distributed for free in august of 2017, and after 4 long years, and are now worth millions. Bunks were released feb of 2021 and cost 1 bnb to mint




Problem:


Bunks is community-driven project. Now we have no dev. 

Token type is bep20. pancakeswap nft market requires bep721. 

Bunks is needed “support wrapping (bep20->bep721)” or “listing bep20 type nft”. 


If pancakeswap supports “wrapping bunk” or “listing bep20 type nft, it’s good for everyone.




If bunk is listed pancakeswap nft market, it has large volume.
choices: YES BSC BUNKS LISTING ON PANCAKESWAP
